<div class="container">
	
	<div class="hero-unit" style = "padding-top: 20px; width: 950px;">
      <h1>Welcome to Task Reminder</h1>
	  <br/>
      <p>Task Reminder was designed to help you keep up with all those essential tasks and chores that need to be done regularly. When life gets busy and these tasks start to slip your mind, Task Reminder stays on top of you by keeping track of when your tasks need to be done, texting you reminders when necessary. The best part is that everything is managed through texting. Once you've added your tasks and settings online, you can manage everything through texting! It's hassle-free, simple, and incredibly effective! Sign up now and easily stay on top of your routine!</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href = "/home/about">How It Works</a>
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href = "#register">Register Now!</a>

	</div>

