      <div class="span6">
        <h2>Receive Text Reminders</h2>
        <p>Task Reminder will text you a reminder message in the morning when your tasks need to be done. If a task is being neglected, Task Reminder will send multiple reminders to ensure that it gets done. It will keep your life organized, and stay on top of you until you've finish all your tasks! </p>
		<img src = "/reminder.jpg" width = "200px">
		<img src = "/overdue.jpg" width = "200px">
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <h2>Update Tasks Via Text</h2>
        <p>When you register, Task Reminder assigns you a number, and always texts you with this number. Communicate with the system by simply texting this number. Let it know that you've completed a task, or request to see all your tasks. It's simply, easy, and no smart phone required! </p>
